{"tid":1901314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CLS, 武漢將捐助食物銷毀,令糧價卻居高不下","createTime":"2020-02-27T17:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T14:50:14.000Z","uid":165361,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3001d8ae6769ff81c065d7b10a29b78b4adc3f","tid":1901314,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:59:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AswrWMhF0ZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAswrWMhF0ZQ&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2dc4a2d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AswrWMhF0ZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n過去一個月來，網上不斷傳出武漢地區銷毀新鮮食物的視頻。本台記者詢問過當地志願組織工作人員，才發現原來當局為保證國營和大企業提供的糧食，能保持在較高價格，以彌補高昂的運輸成本，故不惜銷毀從外省捐助過來的食物，這樣造成了極大的浪費。而另一方面醫院病人的餐費就不斷上漲，市面糧食價格亦居高不下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係CLS"},{"pid":"9ef418f9fda1415757a67c8aaecfe240f4fbe3d1","tid":1901314,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"到時真係無得食咪撚係度叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6610e139116d785db38287c6152b315dfd1b6e","tid":1901314,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ea0bc4181226c2af63f4e14aa043e73c1040f0","tid":1901314,"uid":56627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"國難財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba3860fa198c150c12745ce82e1387d75931fba","tid":1901314,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"浪費食物者生仔冇屎忽"},{"pid":"3117f750ce74d548d6b9fe070c61df24ca240f30","tid":1901314,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:19:45.000Z","msg":"多難興邦